commit.message: Bump to v4.2.0

Update terminatorX logo

Replaced the dated anjuta screenshot with a Linux flavored PE
reference. Also adding some more details to the vinyl.
Add a workflow to build tarballs
Add new target to build .gz and bzip2 from the same tarball
Add missing dependency to spec file to fix fc36 build.

configure.ac: Use PKG_CHECK_MODULES to find libxml2

If libxml2 is not found, `configure' falls back to `xml2-config'.

configure.ac: Drop checks for libxml 1.x

libxml2 has been available for more than 20 years.

configure.ac: Allow cross-compiling with pkg-config

PKG_PROG_PKG_CONFIG calls AC_PATH_TOOL when checking for pkg-config.
When cross-compiling, pkg-config is prefixed with the host type.
Fix lower guidline color for the VU meters
Update headers
Fix button compatibility with Yaru
Tweaking the Sinc interpolator
Update to current autotools syntax
Add sinc based sample interpolation
Fix jack related crash on shutdown
Fix clang warnings

Whitespace cleanup
